 Yule?s 27.2 per cent holding in Tide Water Oil. 

 New Delhi, May 25: The government today said the Small and Medium Enterprises Development Bill seeks to provide statutory backing to development programmes for the sector and replace the unwieldly SSI board with a smaller body. 




